text: {'text': "Useless DJ doesn't know how to play latest songs even requested songs by us. Played not likeable songs claiming requests by other guests when it wasn't full house. One guy kept on pushing n insisting to us to buy a bottle with discount but it was too hard selling, didn't give us space n time to breathe n discuss amongst ourselves, there were 5 of us. Lastly, it was just too expensive, for a can of coke charging at $15 plus have to pay for gst n service charge too separately when we picked up the can of coke ourselves at the bar, where is the service charge in that ? Ridiculous n never even refund to us when we disputed. Never coming back again, thank you very much for this experience", 'languageCode': 'en'}
